APPEALS ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW

2006-0502. State v. Moore.

Cuyahoga App. No. 85828, 2006-Ohio-277. Discretionary cross-appeal accepted on Proposition of Law Nos. II and III; cause held for the decision in 2006-0294 and 2006-0298, State v. Crager, Marion App. No. 9-04-54, 2005-Ohio-6868; and briefing schedule stayed.
